title: Kansas City Royals advance to World Series, beating Toronto Blue Jays 4-3 in Game 6 of ALCS
text:
Kansas City Royals advance to World Series, beating Toronto Blue Jays 4-3 in Game 6 of ALCS By   12:17 a.m., Saturday, October 24, 2015 
KANSAS CITY, Mo. (AP) - Kansas City Royals advance to World Series, beating Toronto Blue Jays 4-3 in Game 6 of ALCS.
